reviews.text: They never fix the leaking air conditioning problem. It's such a hardazous place to dance on wet floor

One of my favorite places in Hong Kong.
Staff always friendly and wonderful atmosphere! Recommend to anyone !
A low key and relax place for salsa and bachata dancing. The people running bachata party here are supper friendly. Fun night dancing in Hong Kong.

Love the place, very friendly environment and staff. Very good place to hang out with friends. You can dance, play pool, darts, beer ping-pong, smoke shisha, so many things to do. Every Wednesday and Sunday, you can dance Bachata and Salsa here. They can make very delicious cocktail at a reasonable price. I strongly recommend you come to have fun with friends in this super friendly bar in the center of Lan Kwai Fong, Hong Kong!
Very cosy place with salsa parties on Sundays.
